OL,3,CHead teachers declare 'trade dispute'
OL,4,Cwith Stormont
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's head teachers have
OL,7,Fwarned of the pressures they are
OL,8,Ffacing bridging the gap between
OL,9,Fnecessities in the classroom and the
OL,10,Flack of funding.
OL,12,FThe National Association of Head
OL,13,FTeachers (NAHT) has declared a "trade
OL,14,Fdispute" with the Department of
OL,15,FEducation and called for the Labour
OL,16,FRelations Agency to facilitate talks.
