OL,3,CHead teachers declare 'trade dispute'
OL,4,Cwith Stormont
OL,6,FThe organisation outlined how teachers
OL,7,Fwere pushed to breaking point with
OL,8,Fheads having to step in to cover
OL,9,Fteaching, "firefighting and holding
OL,10,Fback the floods" to a point that has
OL,11,Fbecome unmanageable.
OL,13,FIt said the system was now failing in
OL,14,Fits duty to provide basic protections
OL,15,Ffor leader and their members could do
OL,16,Fno more. It said the aim of their
OL,17,Faction was to protect children's
OL,18,Feducation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
