OL,3,CHead teachers declare 'trade dispute'
OL,4,Cwith Stormont
OL,6,F"The system has failed to provide
OL,7,Fadequate protections for school
OL,8,Fleaders. It has not protected their
OL,9,Ftime, their workload, their wellbeing,
OL,10,Ftheir safety or their professional
OL,11,Fjudgement. Without that protection,
OL,12,Fleaders cannot protect children.
OL,14,FJoanne Whyte, president of NAHT(NI),
OL,15,Fsaid that school leaders "have nothing
OL,16,Fleft to give".
OL,18,F"They have held the system together
OL,19,Fthrough sheer commitment and
OL,20,Fcompassion, but the weight on their
OL,21,Fshoulders has become intolerable.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
