OL,3,CHead teachers declare 'trade dispute'
OL,4,Cwith Stormont
OL,6,F"When leaders are firefighting broken
OL,7,Fbuildings, carrying unmanageable SEN
OL,8,F(special educational needs) risks,
OL,9,Fcovering classes to save budgets and
OL,10,Fmanaging a rising tide of governance
OL,11,Fand complaints pressures, they cannot
OL,12,Fgive children the leadership they
OL,13,Fdeserve.
