OL,3,CHead teachers declare 'trade dispute'
OL,4,Cwith Stormont
OL,6,FThe union says this is a clear
OL,7,Fadmission that the system can no
OL,8,Flonger provide meaningful protection
OL,9,Ffor school leaders and, therefore,
OL,10,Fcannot guarantee the conditions
OL,11,Fchildren need to thrive.
OL,13,FIn a statement the Department of
OL,14,FEducation said, "It is disappointing
OL,15,Fthat NAHT in Northern Ireland has
OL,16,Ftaken the decision to enter dispute
OL,17,Fwith employers and my Department over
OL,18,Fthe workload of school leaders."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
