OL,6,F"The Minister commissioned an
OL,7,FIndependent Panel last May to look
OL,8,Fspecifically at this issue.
OL,10,F"Since receiving the report from the
OL,11,FPanel at the end of November 2025 work
OL,12,Fhas been ongoing to scope the impact
OL,13,Fof each of the recommendations and map
OL,14,Fout the actions and timescales that
OL,15,Fwould be required to deliver change.
OL,16,FAll teachers and school leaders have
OL,17,Fbeen advised of the proposed next
OL,18,Fsteps including a commitment to
OL,19,Fproduce a detailed action plan by
OL,20,FApril 2026."
