OL,6,F"The Minister and Department have
OL,7,Fshown undoubted commitment to tackling
OL,8,Fexcessive workload and would urge the
OL,9,Funion to agree a resolution to this
OL,10,Fissue. The Department will be engaging
OL,11,Fwith NAHT representatives and the
OL,12,Fwider Northern Ireland Teachers'
OL,13,FCouncil (NITC) through TNC to seek a
OL,14,Fresolution as soon as possible."
